  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.551932569769191        -15.0188          -346.34         -1449.10
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.187166858709926         -5.0931          -117.45          -491.41
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.050356869074914          1.3703            31.60           132.21
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.028568633439249         -0.7774           -17.93           -75.01
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.141164393384260          3.8413            88.58           370.63
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

